oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville Songwriters Association International: November Schedule
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Lyricists;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (green and red on white) announcing the November schedule for the Nashville Songwriters Association International, which is celebrating 30 years of song. The Association's events include performances on November 6 at The Bluebird Cafe, November 14 at the Radio Cafe, November 20 at the Douglas Corner Cafe, and November 23 at The Bluebird Cafe for NSAI Anniversary Writers Night.
